  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >eyeDASH is a bullet hell dungeon crawler in which you play as an ethereal eye. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dash, dodge and break your way in through the caverns</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rescue your spawns for extra-lives</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rediscover the Superdash technique and shatter your enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat the boss and take your revenge on the Sharps! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383060/extras/f73970da460cd49761d6c00f2e635bbb.poster.avif?t=1759940138\" width=410 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383060/extras/f73970da460cd49761d6c00f2e635bbb.webm?t=1759940138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383060/extras/f73970da460cd49761d6c00f2e635bbb.mp4?t=1759940138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383060/extras/dd968f1f3b075876ab092087a7ae66f6.poster.avif?t=1759940138\" width=408 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383060/extras/dd968f1f3b075876ab092087a7ae66f6.webm?t=1759940138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383060/extras/dd968f1f3b075876ab092087a7ae66f6.mp4?t=1759940138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your reflexes will be tested by a fast scaling difficulty - ranging from light exploration to full-on bullet hell. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >16 hand-crafted levels with multiple challenges to conquer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 enemy types</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 unique boss fights</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock Survival (Endless) mode by completing the game</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One last challenge awaits to prove your mastery - beat the game without any extra lives!</p>",
